extendedInfo.directions: Cooking Instructions: Preheat oven to 450 degrees F. Remove Boboli Pizza Crust from the wrapper. Spread some tasty sauce or Evoo on the crust. Decorate with toppings. Place directly on the oven rack or on baking sheet. Bake for 10-15 minutes or until desired crispness. Yum!
